arStrings.szText: Locations on the Map {hotkey:map} marked with {icon:Wardrobe_New_Purchased_Item, 3.0}  contain new purchased items.
Purchased armor, weapon and other character cosmetics are found in the Wardrobe {icon:Marker_Wardrobe, 3.0}
Purchased mounts and mount cosmetics are found in the Stable {icon:Marker_Vendor_Stable, 3.0}
Purchased emotes are found when editing the Action Wheel {icon:Store_Icon_Wheel, 2.0}
